      • oneDown

        public static ComponentFunction oneDown(java.lang.String winname,
                        java.lang.String compname,
                        java.lang.String integerValue)
         
                 Attempts to perform a ScrollLineDown on a scrollbar.

                Attempts to perform a ScrollLineDown on a scrollbar.  The input record 
                can optionally specify the number of iterations to perform the action.
        Supporting Engines:

        • Rational Robot
        • Rational RobotJ
        • Mercury Interactive WinRunner
        • Automated QA TestComplete
        • Google Android
        • OpenQA Selenium
        Parameters:
        winname - Optional:NO The name of the window to act upon.
        compname - Optional:NO The name of the component to act upon.
        integerValue - Optional:YES DefaultVal:1 Optional integer to specify how many times to perform the action.
